videoSnippet.title: Complete Madness | Aronian vs Mamedyarov | Batumi Chess Olympiad (2018)
videoSnippet.description:

Levon Aronian vs Shakhriyar Mamedyarov
43rd Chess Olympiad (2018), rd 5, Sep-28 
Spanish Game: Open. Open Variation (C80)
